'''Italian Studies''' is an [[Interdisciplinarity|interdisciplinary field]] dealing with the study of the Italian [[italian language|language]], [[Italian literature|literature]], [[Italian art|art]], [[Italian history|history]], [[Italian politics|politics]], [[Italian culture|culture]] and society.

