{{Infobox military structure | name=Padma Cantonment | location= [[Munshiganj District|Munshiganj]] and [[Shariatpur District]]s, [[Bangladesh]] | coordinates= | image= | caption= | type= [[Cantonment]] | built= | materials= | used= | controlledby=[[Bangladesh Army]] | garrison= | current_commander= | battles= }}
'''Padma Cantonment''' is a Bangladeshi military cantonment near under-construction [[Padma Bridge]] in [[Munshiganj District|Munshiganj]] and [[Shariatpur District]]s, [[Bangladesh]].<ref>{{cite web|title=New cantonment by Padma bridge|url=http://www.thedailystar.net/new-cantonment-by-padma-bridge-50039|website=The Daily Star|date=13 November 2014}}</ref> The cantonment has been named in line with the name of Padma Bridge. It has been established to ensure overall security of the bridge as it will be the main link of the highway connectivity between [[South Bengal]] and other parts of Bangladesh.
==Units== * [[99th Composite Brigade (Bangladesh)|99th Composite Brigade]]
