The '''Roman Catholic Diocese of Yokohama''' ({{lang-la|Yokohamaen(sis)}}, {{lang-ja|カトリック横浜教区}}) is a [[diocese]] located in the city of [[Yokohama]] in the [[Ecclesiastical province]] of [[Roman Catholic Archdiocese of Tokyo|Tokyo]] in Japan.
==History== * November 11, 1937: Established as Diocese of Yokohama from the [[Metropolitan Archdiocese of Tōkyō]]
